---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <div class="text-sm font-light">
      <p>
        Hi, I'm Ashmith, a Product Security Intern at Vontier passionate about cybersecurity, ethical hacking, and AI-driven security automation.
        <br />
        My expertise includes:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Penetration Testing & Ethical Hacking</li>
        <li>Security Automation & AI Integration</li>
        <li>Vulnerability Assessment & Management</li>
        <li>Network Security & Packet Analysis</li>
        <li>Python & Security Tooling</li>
        <li>Cloud Security</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      Highly driven and curious, I constantly push myself to learn and build. When not in security research, I challenge myself through long-distance running and maintain discipline in both technical and personal goals.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      I believe in the power of security-by-design and shifting left, integrating security practices early in the development lifecycle to build robust, secure products that customers can trust.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
